  ID: Fra Giacomo, Hospitaller men-at-arms
  Name: Anselm
  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  Description: "He prides himself on discipline and contempt for pain. The younger
    recruits fear his temper more than the Ottoman guns. A Turkish arrow smashed
    into his thigh and splintered the femur \u2014 when he tries to stand, the bone
    shifts like wet bark.\n\nTreatment: Cut the shaft, expose the entry, and use
    forceps to remove only what you can see. Any deeper digging risks snapping the
    artery. You align the leg and splint it tight. He won\u2019t walk without a cane,
    if he walks again at all."
